        # [markdown-katex][repo_ref]
        
        This is an extension for [Python Markdown](https://python-markdown.github.io/)
        which adds [KaTeX](https://katex.org/) support.
        
            ```math
            f(x) = \int_{-\infty}^\infty
                \hat f(\xi)\,e^{2 \pi i \xi x}
                \,d\xi
            ```
        
